_sText: ABOUT THE RELEASE: This is the Alpha release of my concept map, fy_tripview. ================================================= ABOUT THE MAP: Max Players: 32 slots Ideal Players: 16 The map consists of three levels with one hallway, The hallway's floors and ceilings are made of bulletproof glass, so you always know where your enemies are, but what can you do to get to them? It is a phychological map and requires you to use team communication to kill your enemies. So how good is your clan's communication? ================================================= Contents of this Package : fy_tripview.BSP ================================================= Installation Instructions : Unzip contents Copy "cstrike" into C:\Program Files\Steam\SteamApps\YOURNAME\counter-strike source\ ================================================= <<< M3-Knifely >>> Please leave me some feedback at my email : M3knifely@gmail.com Game On
